哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"7d4c586c77a9776811cb6278dab9ddd6","url_token":"bi-luo-liang-feng-92-89","name":"笔落惊风","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-bb51936fa7f92c8263e2f1277cddeb60_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-bb51936fa7f92c8263e2f1277cddeb60_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/7d4c586c77a9776811cb6278dab9ddd6","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563576830","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546252744,"updated_time":1546252744,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e我想先给答主讲一个我自己的故事\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我四年级时知道了什么是哥德巴赫猜想，也知道了加法的奇偶性。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e于是我就错误的认为，因为任何两个奇数相加都是偶数，而所有比二大的素数都是奇数，所以任何一个偶数可以拆分为两个素数之和……\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e当然这是很蠢的想法，但是当时我兴奋的去跟数学老师说了自己的想法，然后我的梦想破灭了。但是我从来不以为耻，因为这是非常可贵的研究数学时的品质，就是敢于追寻的勇气。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我们知道研究数学最重要的不是天赋，而是勇气，理性，洞察，奉献，高洁，超越。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果证明同学不是蹭热度或者哗众取宠，那我只能说，真理的钥匙在你的手中。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e非常抱歉自己偏题了，但我还要多加几句:科学的殿堂需要极高的素养，真理的圣光也只有博学多识者才有资格沐浴。你现在手握着钥匙，但古往今来无数人都做到了这一点，而成功者寥若晨星。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563533337,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"a2e0fa8bb0b012d84cc4e2ab2c743489","url_token":"zhao-bu-dong-64-74","name":"赵不懂","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-3161a407bf836ec2c4474c7f9ac5c22c_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-3161a407bf836ec2c4474c7f9ac5c22c_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/a2e0fa8bb0b012d84cc4e2ab2c743489","user_type":"people","headline":"资深学渣","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563533337","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546247498,"updated_time":1546247498,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"这两天天天被推荐这个。。。。\u003cbr\u003e不过好在明天就是一号了，就可以看到最后的论文了。虽然我可能看不出来他证明的对不对。\u003cbr\u003e只想说一个点，高中学生你的数学水平能到什么程度？自学到什么了？如果用常规的方法证明肯定是轮不到你的，况且你也没掌握这些，对不对？那只能用你自学的那些所谓的高等数学来证明？可是高等数学并不高等啊同学。就好像我只掌握了百以内加减法就去做高考数学最后一道大题一样啊。\u003cbr\u003e我只是一个普通学校的学习特别差的数学专业学生，真的建议你先别想这些，陈景润证明了几年？你才学了几年数学？我五子棋下的特别好能不能围棋打败柯洁？","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563532877,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"ce5ed88c7b6b1e45cb6eb875d2f296be","url_token":"li-bai-tian-de-li-bai-68","name":"礼拜天的李白","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-d16ba4fe31e08732835f7dd6a7bf2bc2_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-d16ba4fe31e08732835f7dd6a7bf2bc2_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/ce5ed88c7b6b1e45cb6eb875d2f296be","user_type":"people","headline":"学生","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563532877","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546247449,"updated_time":1546247449,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e他能获得教授称号\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563444065,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question