i/v4/answers/563261791","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546218405,"updated_time":1546218405,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e同学如果你是真的那种百年一遇的天才，高中就证明出来了，那就肯定不止清华要你了，全世界的研究所和顶尖大学都会争着要你。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果你不是上面那种情况，别想了，好好学吧，哥德巴赫猜想还有黎曼猜想这样的没有经过高等数学的熏陶是绝对没戏的，绝对是天方夜谭。它们都是问题描述很简洁，但要证明出来不知道要费多少力气，全世界优秀的数学家都没能解决的问题，怎么可能你在高中那几年就证明出来，真的是不切实际。好好学习，不好高骛远，此乃正道。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563197051,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"cd392f9529150a0a6247589eb76c429b","url_token":"wang-dong-dong-54-43","name":"冬冬","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/cd392f9529150a0a6247589eb76c429b","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563197051","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546192917,"updated_time":1546192917,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e不但能，而且能清华北大两开花！\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563166637,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"8a4fe51246826925dc163b933670c976","url_token":"zi-yi-xiu-xing-52","name":"自倚修行","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/8a4fe51246826925dc163b933670c976","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563166637","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546188205,"updated_time":1546188205,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e不会，不管你是不是真的证明了，报送政策很严的，没有证哥猜这一项，所以你可以放弃报送进清北的幻想了，但你依旧可以通过高考进去。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563039917,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"616583f1af7642b6cffd0878a5cd638d","url_token":"infatuate-27","name":"Infatuate","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-a2393d0b1f9977f4effafb64c05ec787_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-a2393d0b1f9977f4effafb64c05ec787_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/616583f1af7642b6cffd0878a5cd638d","user_type":"people","headline":"学生","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563039917","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546175764,"updated_time":1546175764,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e拙见。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e首先，证明哥德巴赫猜想需要的知识容量能不能在三年之内学完这是第一个问题。其次，这个东西的难度远高于数竞。如果你的目标是清北，那你大可以选择去数竞。又或者如果你的目标是证明哥德巴赫猜想，那你也应该搞数竞，因为考一个好的学校，好的教授来带领你，远胜过你独自研究三年失败后，然后别人花两年就赶超你。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563030858,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563030858","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546174704,"updated_time":1546174704,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e        这个应该不是报送不报送的问题，是选择是去清华还是北大当博导的问题。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e       攻克 数学难题不是买彩票看运气的，他人千辛万苦攻克不了的难关不是某个没有接受过系统性学习的天才能灵光乍现就能解决的，如果一个高中生解决了只有三种可能。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e         1天才，这个天才之前未曾有，之后也几乎不可能有。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e         2穿越者，他来自一个已经借出猜想的时代并背会了证明全过程，看来他记忆力不错，数学功底也至少达到了硕士研究生水平。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e         3这兄弟是tm骗子。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563022213,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"a6b3d4f0649b74dff67da4dc477d30ee","url_token":"wo-de-mao-pao-dao-na-li-qu-liao","name":"我的猫跑到哪里去了","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-2db3f54962ac35c20969a53e2da8af31_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-2db3f54962ac35c20969a53e2da8af31_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/a6b3d4f0649b74dff67da4dc477d30ee","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://w